The package boost-function-types is compatible with built-in CMake targets of FindBoost.cmake:

    find_package(Boost REQUIRED COMPONENTS function_types)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::function_types)

or the generated cmake configs via:

    find_package(boost_function_types REQUIRED CONFIG)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::function_types)
